      </p>

     </div>
     <div id="fn" class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#PJA10d272n1-ptr" id="PJA10d272n1">1</a>
      
   <p>On this <a href="default.xqy?keys=ADMS-print-06-10-03-0001-0159" class="document">day</a> <abbr title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ John Adams (17351826) ]">JA</abbr> also wrote to William Lee at Brussels to introduce Francis Dana (<abbr title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ letterbook copy (Letterbook copies are normally unsigned, but any such copy is assumed to be in the hand of the person responsible for the text unless it is otherwise described.) ]">LbC</abbr>, <span class="ref-terms">Adams Papers</span>).</p>

     </div>
     <div class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#PJA10d272n2-ptr" id="PJA10d272n2">2</a>
      
   <p>A copying omission, supplied from the Letterbook.</p>

